<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>About Us!</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="Width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #262626;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .loader {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            text-align: center; /* Center-aligns the text */
            color: #fff; /* Sets text color to white */
        }

        .loader h1 {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 9em;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            background-image: url(https://www.maptive.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Pin-Map-mapping-software-e1596147662648.jpg);
            background-repeat: repeat-x;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            animation: animate 15s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes animate {
            0% {
                background-position: left 0px top 80px;
            }
            40% {
                background-position: left 800px top -50px;
            }
            80% {
                background-position: left 1800px top -50px;
            }
            100% {
                background-position: left 2400px top 80px;
            }
        }

        .loader p {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: white; /* Ensures the text color is white */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="loader">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
            Our locations are based nationwide, allowing us to offer
            all of our services to achieve the highest level of customer satisfaction.
            The customer who buys the most produce from us will get an interview with Mr. Beast!
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
